,Recommended,290340,32275727,Posted: 8 June,all,Xenial-Lynx,"This is one of my favorite games! I love the board-game/RPG inspired gameplay. The tutorial does a great job of introducing the player to the main mechanics at a good pace. I really like the concept of multiple ways to win the game, leading to even more neat strategies for players to come up with. It's a creative twist on a long-standing concept. One thing to keep in mind is that a play session can sometimes run about an hour, but not always, and I actually prefer being able to sit down and play a game for a long time. I would definitely recommend Armello."
