,Recommended,290340,17222779,"Posted: 25 July, 2015",all,Lowrater,"Armello is a turn-based game with cards and cubes with 4 different heroes, with different stats and abilitys where you have to win the kings trust and get retribution of citys while defending your self agens 3 other players either locally with AI or online, while deadly banes sneaking close to you to stand in the way.We have 4 heroes to play as. Thane the wolf, Mercurio the rat, Sana the bear or Amber the bunny. Each hero has it own stats and what their specialty is. Every player has 3 Ap start points (Points to move around the map). When you have picked a hero, you can choose a ring which will give +1 in a stat. When you're in the game, you can choose between 3 quests, and after that there wil be displayed your flag over a area you need to take care of to also recieve your quest items etc. Besides this, there is instances that gives loot, money etc. At night ""banes"" will come out of the instances and will hunt every city and player on the map.The cards gives you a overview of what you can do. Either you pick Item, Spell or Trickery. You need to be aware of what cards you have to win the fights and every card you pick might have a negative effect. If you spend your inventory on cards, you will lose cubes to throw, since they stand for the same. Be aware that some cards need gold before it can be used. The cards can also be throwed at your enemies or on your self or over citys to make traps, effect, health, damage etc. Making traps will show a icon on the area you placed.Besides all this, there is 3 types of gamemodes while playing to win the game. Each player can have it's own tactic and do the same. Either you:  1. Be a king slayer, 2. Spirit s tone victory, or 3. Prestige victory. The king has 7 health and is loseing 1 each day, when he dies some one need to take his place, but the kingdom is guarded by kings guard. If you kill or attack kings guard, the king will set a bounty on your head where every kings guard will follow you. Each game can last up to 60 mins, so you have much to look forward too!Besides what i've written so far, you can already see that the game has much to offer. If you have a hard time under the game, you can always press ESC and re-read the information you got in the first place to get a re-cap. I can gladly recommend this of it's huge amount of quality of content and playtime.Here is a demo:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7I_zoD3lohg"
