 problems with this game.  I haven't run into any bugs yet, and it seems the devs are constantly updating it to make sure it looks even better than its' original launch state.  I fully support this game, and once again I'm just gonna say, it gets a 10/10 from me.  There is one thing I want to say to the devs right now, just from me personally; I don't speak for the other fans of this game.  PLEASE, make an expansion!  I'll buy it, the other fans might buy it; I'm spreading the word about this game as much as I can.Thank you"
