76561198079154733,Recommended,290340,17947197,"Posted: 8 September, 2015",all,Sorry Stoat,"A turn-based digital board game set in a disney's Robin Hood like world where anphropomorphic animals rule the land. Whether playing single player or multiplayer; the game consists of 4 heroes vying for the future of the throne. The game is easy to learn but difficult to master. The board is randomly generated (except starting points and the palace) with each terrain having a different effect on the game and your hero. Settlements generate gold, mountains require double the movement, swamps cost health to traverse, forests provide stealth at night, stone circles heal the uncorrupted and dungeons can help or hinder you. Time is limited by the king's decaying health and turns alternate between dawn and dusk each providing different benefits.Not finished, work in progress."
