76561197973589694,Recommended,290340,16316584,"Posted: 11 June, 2015",all,MightyFox,"There are already plenty of reviews stating what this game is, so I'll skip that part. The real question is, is it enjoyable, and the answer is a resounding yes. Is it worth 25 USD? Well...Being early access there are still a few kinks I feel the game needs to work out, but the developers are constantly tweaking the game to make it as fair for all players and strategies as possible. New characters can currently be previewed in game and on the forums, so the current four are certainly not the end all, and more content and game modes are still being worked on. Multiplayer is operating, though it's currently easier to schedule a time with friends than wait for a public match. Single player is still a hoot though, and will keep you busy for hours as you try and achieve the different win conditions for in-game rewards that can be used in multiplayer matches. Artwork and design is also stunningly beautiful. For what's there, 25 may seem a little steep, but for what's promised, 25 is well worth it."
